C<pre><code>// 计算Fibonacci的空间复杂度？
long long* Fibonacci(int n)
{
    if (n == 0)
        return;
    long long* fibArray = (long long*)malloc((n + 1) * sizeof(long long));
    fibArray[0] = 0;
    fibArray[1] = 1;
    for (int i = 2; i &lt;= n; ++i)
    {
        fibArray[i] = fibArray[i - 1] + fibArray[i - 2];
    }
    return fibArray;
}
</code></pre> <p>动态开辟了N个空间，空间复杂度为 O(N)</p>

